EN: Riding a bike along the river to admire the beautiful scenery is a pleasure.

ZH: 每一个季节都有不同的景色。
EN: Each season has different scenery.

ZH: 山下的景色非常壮观。
EN: The scenery below the mountain is very spectacular.

ZH: 在清晨，湖水倒影着远山的景色。
EN: In the morning, the lake reflects the scenery of the distant mountains.

